{"tid":1327462,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［有冇得諗］貼紋身貼紙抗爭  一走即刻捽甩佢","createTime":"2019-07-17T15:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T15:22:55.000Z","uid":154627,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fb64cd2221c36c871b1a610ea66728667407574f","tid":1327462,"uid":154627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:11:06.000Z","msg":"次次抗爭都有人露紋身  好易比狗認到<br />\n大家一齊痴紋身貼紙  走個時捽甩佢<br />\n一方面做cover <br />\n一方面比藉口話啲片個個唔係自己<br />\n有冇得諗?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe14ed2d0f37fe9eebf90e2e1601652a78a926e5","tid":1327462,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:22:55.000Z","msg":"[721見] 如何正確隱藏身份 (整合+進階篇)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327279</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9Pobuw7Wk2k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9Pobuw7Wk2k&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQshSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=1e94443a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9Pobuw7Wk2k</a> <br />\n唔想專登買面罩其實用Tee都得<br />\n<br />\n✅ DNS用1.1.1.1（尤其係3HK、HKT用戶）<br />\n✅ 上討論區用Tor Browser，但唔好用Tor Browser Login 任何帳號<br />\n✅ P2P通訊用Telegram / Signal<br />\n✅ Group通訊用Signal<br />\n✅ 即時戰略遊戲用Playstation Message傾<br />\n✅ 電話唔好用指紋/面容解鎖<br />\n✅ 重要嘢面談<br />\n✅ 食煙嘅你買個打火機同包純薄萬傍身<br />\n✅ 飲酒嘅你飲樽裝好飲過罐裝<br />\n✅ 有時毒撚一個更開心，唔洗吓吓同人一齊玩<br />\n✅ 毒撚自己一個玩，唔好去多狗地方玩<br />\n<br />\n❌ 咪撚帶八達通同信用卡<br />\n❌ 咪撚著拖鞋短褲同容易辨認嘅衣物<br />\n❌ 咪撚咁傻仔帶啲唔合理嘅物品係身，例如拍戲道具<br />\n❌ 咪撚除/拉低口罩<br />\n❌ 咪撚影人樣，影狗同影景就夠<br />\n<br />\n❗關閉電話上所有Facebook、WhatsApp同Instagram權限<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1629975780370609/posts/2528022960565882?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1629975780370609%2Fposts%2F2528022960565882%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQshSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=e99d5925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1629975780370609/posts/2528022960565882?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://github.com/cybersec-hk/digital_awareness_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fcybersec-hk%2Fdigital_awareness_hk&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQshSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=c44c9000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">github.com/cybersec-hk/digital_awareness_hk</a>"}]}